---
import BaseLayout from "../../components/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="BillLoopr - MrFung" description="BillLoopr support and privacy entry in Chinese and English.">
  <Hero
    home
    kicker="Billable Time · Projects · Invoices"
    title="BillLoopr"
    zh="面向独立工作者的计费工时、项目记录和发票准备工具。"
    en="Billable time tracking, project records, and invoice preparation for independent professionals."
  >
    <div class="mf-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="/billloopr/support/">支持 / Support</a>
      <a class="button" href="/billloopr/privacy/">隐私政策 / Privacy</a>
    </div>
  </Hero>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>工作记录更清楚 / Clearer Billing Records</h2>
        <p>从计时、客户、项目到发票准备，把计费工作需要回看的上下文集中管理。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Timer</small>
            <h3>计时 / Timer</h3>
            <p>记录可计费工作时段，保留项目、费率、货币和预计时长进度。</p>
            <p>Record billable sessions with project context, rates, currencies, and planned-time progress.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>Records</small>
            <h3>检索 / Find</h3>
            <p>客户、项目、发票和时间记录支持更清晰的搜索、筛选、预览和删除流程。</p>
            <p>Clients, projects, invoices, and time entries are designed around search, filtering, preview, and safe deletion.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <div>
            <small>App Store</small>
            <h3>公开页面 / Public Pages</h3>
            <p>隐私、支持、数据删除和联系信息以中英双语公开展示。</p>
            <p>Privacy, support, data deletion, and contact information are available in Chinese and English.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>隐私政策</h3>
          <p>BillLoopr 不需要账号即可使用，主要数据保存在设备本地，导出和分享由用户主动触发。</p>
          <p><a href="/billloopr/privacy/">查看隐私政策</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
          <p>BillLoopr works without an account. App records are stored locally unless the user chooses to export or share them.</p>
          <p><a href="/billloopr/privacy/">Read privacy policy</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
